{"tid":1571051,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【按摩遇淫more】與男友去按摩僅相隔布廉　台女被按摩師性侵不敢出聲","createTime":"2019-09-15T10:08:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T17:37:10.000Z","uid":175314,"like":9,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e5fa74285b17689564cd439c7fae3848ec9efbfe","tid":1571051,"uid":175314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:08:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2451815/?r=mcsdfb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2451815%2F%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb&d=02TnLe2cOfQrY9jdqtoXef5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=28758559\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2451815/?r=mcsdfb</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台北驚傳女大學生按摩店被性侵案，一名女大學生日前與男友一同到按摩店按摩，她與男友僅相隔一塊布簾距離，豈料按摩期間被按摩師性侵，她嚇得不敢出聲，令按摩師得逞。該名女生翌日才向男友哭訴，涉案按摩師其後被警方逮捕，案件正在進一步調查中。<br />\n<br />\n與男友僅相隔布廉<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">據台媒報道，事發於上周一晚上10時許，被性侵的女大學生花花（化名）與男友到當地一間按摩店，並由31歲的阮姓男子進行全身按摩服務，期間阮男為一逞私慾，性侵只和男友相隔一塊布簾、不到5米距離的花花，由於花花當時嚇得，而不敢出聲，遂被強制性侵得逞。</span><br />\n<br />\n花花與男友離開按摩店後，直到翌日，她才情緒崩潰的向男友泣訴，並在男友陪同下，前往醫院驗傷，再到北市婦幼隊做筆錄。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">警方受理案件，逮捕涉案的阮男，調查發現，阮男從2014年來到台灣，2017年成為逃逸移工，冒用他人的身分證到按摩店擔任按摩師。阮男到案時供稱，花花當時並沒有明顯抗拒，因此認為與花花是合意性交，而檢察官最後依強制性交罪將阮男聲請羈押獲准。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講真，條女如果唔係啞嘅，被人攪完走去告人，其實係咪嫌人哋服務唔夠好咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6edec3c181c9306e51306cd3c2290545adce10cb","tid":1571051,"uid":52939,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:09:16.000Z","msg":"Av"},{"pid":"caaec3848792ca89ff48422be3b99d0425ae58a2","tid":1571051,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:09:37.000Z","msg":"Av <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1fb4e0fb52a24ec66acab7f797a0c8022d5fd4a","tid":1571051,"uid":41508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:12:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14c61c15e97237684da26b422398abb706bc9ec8","tid":1571051,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:12:30.000Z","msg":"根本好享受"},{"pid":"479539a0cf3e0f97ea6b6f5f8e1cc37c0c3fb682","tid":1571051,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:18:21.000Z","msg":"Code？"},{"pid":"32ce98af9c48da8ed2dd6e7c17766b9682505974","tid":1571051,"uid":175314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14c61c15e97237684da26b422398abb706bc9ec8","tid":1571051,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:12:30.000Z","msg":"根本好享受"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2de379d4bda4794df515209bd7f1a7a58cae6bb7","tid":1571051,"uid":203889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:22:42.000Z","msg":"屌我諗起女義士單野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔該唔好係真"},{"pid":"d9d87ba5095d0042ac25e717e3283183d67ec420","tid":1571051,"uid":135867,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:25:16.000Z","msg":"今舖真係AV劇情"},{"pid":"59519078ebf3f1a6c1c625b853758a563d00f605","tid":1571051,"uid":175314,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2de379d4bda4794df515209bd7f1a7a58cae6bb7","tid":1571051,"uid":203889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:22:42.000Z","msg":"屌我諗起女義士單野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔該唔好係真"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:30:26.000Z","msg":"飯焦嚟㗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5540d53158d92f0bb183f30